<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Jul1936"><font color="red">7 July 1936</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from T.S. Eliot to Paul L&eacute;on): [Want] news &hellip; progress of Part II &hellip; I do not know whether Joyce has found conditions more favourable for working than when I saw him a month ago. </div>
